  m_Name: prince_william_bubba_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Elementborn.Game.NpcConversationProfile
  NpcName: Prince William
  Role: 'Prince of the Metal Capital in Metal Capital. Role: RoyalFamily.'
  Personality: Friendly, energetic, and more practical than formal.
  LocalKnowledge: I am usually found at Chrome Court Workshops in Metal Capital.
    Son of Queen Rhonda and King Randy.
  Boundaries: Do not reveal hidden plot secrets unless the player has earned them
    through quests.
  Greeting: Welcome. I am Prince William.
  UnknownResponse: That is not something I can speak on yet, but the city has many
    stories for those who listen.
  KeywordResponses:
  - Keyword: element
    Response: My element is Metal.
  - Keyword: family
    Response: Son of Queen Rhonda and King Randy.
  - Keyword: where
    Response: You can find me at Chrome Court Workshops in Metal Capital.
  - Keyword: capital
    Response: The Metal Capital is strong because its people endure, learn, and build
      together.
